    <title>Introduction</title>

    <p>
        The goal of the Getting Started with Foresight Linux User Guide is to
        provide a high level overview of using Foresight Linux, including the
        <app>Conary</app> package manager, for users new to Linux or Foresight.
    </p>
    <p>
        The User Guide also provides an overview of commonly used applications,
        customizing your new installation, adding and removing software, and 
        tips on getting help.
    </p>

